parameters.name: endTime
parameters.description: The end time to list in UTC. The operation will return an ephemeris if its expiration time is within the time range defined by the startTime and endTime.

parameters.name: satelliteId
parameters.description: The AWS Ground Station satellite ID to list ephemeris for.

parameters.name: startTime
parameters.description: The start time to list in UTC. The operation will return an ephemeris if its expiration time is within the time range defined by the startTime and endTime.

parameters.name: statusList
parameters.description: The list of ephemeris status to return. (string) ---

nested_items.name: creationTime
nested_items.description: The time the ephemeris was uploaded in UTC.

nested_items.name: enabled
nested_items.description: Whether or not the ephemeris is enabled.

nested_items.name: ephemerisId
nested_items.description: The AWS Ground Station ephemeris ID.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: A name string associated with the ephemeris. Used as a human-readable identifier for the ephemeris.

nested_items.name: priority
nested_items.description: Customer-provided priority score to establish the order in which overlapping ephemerides should be used.

nested_items.name: sourceS3Object
nested_items.description: Source S3 object used for the ephemeris.

nested_items.name: key
nested_items.description: An Amazon S3 key for the ephemeris.

nested_items.name: version
nested_items.description: For versioned S3 objects, the version to use for the ephemeris.
